query.pigql: q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'IsClosed' == "true"; q = group q by 'First_Contact_Close__c'; q = foreach q generate 'First_Contact_Close__c' as 'First_Contact_Close__c', count() as 'count', (count()) / sum(count()) over([..] partition by all)*100 as 'perc_Percent'; q = filter q by 'First_Contact_Close__c' == "true";

q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'IsClosed' == "true"; q = group q by all; q = foreach q generate avg('{{column(Static_Duration.selection, ["pigql_value"]).asObject()}}') as 'avg_Time_Open__c';

lens_table.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q=filter q by 'IsClosed' == "true";q = foreach q generate 'CaseNumber', first('Account_Name') as 'Account_Name', first('CSAT__c') as 'CSAT__c',  first('First_Contact_Close__c') as 'First_Contact_Close__c', first('Type') as 'Type', first('Owner_Name') as 'Owner_Name', first('MilestoneStatus__c') as 'MilestoneStatus__c', avg('{{column(Static_Duration.selection, ["pigql_value"]).asObject()}}') as '{{column(Static_Duration.selection, ["measure_field"]).asObject()}}', first('Origin') as 'Origin', first('Priority') as 'Priority', first('Status') as 'Status', first('Type_of_Support__c') as 'Type_of_Support__c', first('IsEscalated') as 'Escalated'; q = order q by 'CaseNumber' desc; q = limit q 100;
